item.title: Prayer bpn12399 in Namibia
item.description: *(Hoa khoen Elob din ge I//kha-i as gose //in di !asa ni u-/khi. Elob ge khoe-e !na ≠am hase //gui ai tama ha. Netii !norasa mas ge hoa /khaga xu ma ≠gomsabei hoae xuni u-/khihe. A khoetse Elob ditse. ≠Gom //awosa u-hare netii !norasa mas ta ha xutse nesis ga !hanasisens, ≠harogus gas xawets ge /khaihe hase ni I tsini /arobahe-//nai !norasasiba xura mai ge disi-!naguse ni !kho-!oa. Ega-/geb ose I !
